name: Wolf Shirt Mens Unisex Hand Screen Print American Apparel Crew Neck
description:
Designed and hand pressed in California by Couth. Printed on American Apparel’s Fine Jersey Short Sleeve T Fine Jersey (100% Cotton) construction (Heather Grey contains 10% Polyester).

How to order:

Please Select your T-shirt’s size and color at checkout and leave us a note and be sure to use size chart and color availability.
Available sizes: S, M, L, XL, XXL

We use water base ink and discharge base ink that gives the shirt a very soft feel. We hand screen print each shirt to ensure quality

Please let us know if you have a preferred color.

We custom print your T-shirts after receiving your order and confirmation of payment, because our tshirts are made to order it takes us 2-5 business days to finish your T-shirts and they are shipped immediately.

We accept returns and exchanges as long as they are in new condition

We stay 100% behind our product and if for any reason you are not satisfied with our product please contact us

If you have more questions please check our policy page.

Thank you for your interest in our shop and stop by our Storefront for our entire lineup

We also have an Etsy store
https://www.etsy.com/shop/Couthclothing
